    {
      "id": "sybil_26_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_26",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning, showroom-ready condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it\u2019s never seen a speck of dirt. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one. Come take a look and fall in love!",
