      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_24_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_24",
      "description": "A masterclass in analog engineering, this E46 M3 features the high-revving S54B32 power plant, complete with individual throttle bodies and a factory-rated 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, providing surgical precision on the limit. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a complete VANOS overhaul. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from refreshed bushings and dampers, while the exterior finish and interior ergonomics remain in showroom state. A definitive driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
      "price": 47500.0,
